1.name: DUNS (Data Universal Numbering System)

4.name: IATA (International Air Transport Association)
4.desc: Partner identification code assigned by the International Air Transport Association.

5.name: INSEE (Institut National de la Statistique et des Etudes Economiques) - SIRET
5.desc: French national statistics institute. SIRET means Systeme Informatique du Repertoire des entreprises et de leurs ETablissements.

8.name: UCC Communications ID (Uniform Code Council Communications Identifier)
8.desc: The Uniform Code Council Communications Identifier is a ten digit code used to uniquely identify physical and logical locations.

9.name: DUNS (Data Universal Numbering System) with 4 digit suffix

12.name: Telephone number
12.desc: Partner identification code corresponds to the partner telephone number.

14.desc: Partner identification code assigned by EAN International, an international organization of EAN Member Organizations, that along with the Uniform Code Council manages the EAN.UCC System (a series of standards for supply chain management).

18.name: AIAG (Automotive Industry Action Group)
18.desc: Partner identification code assigned by the Automotive Industry Action Group.

22.name: INSEE (Institut National de la Statistique et des Etudes Economiques) - SIREN
22.desc: French national statistics institute. SIREN means Systeme Informatique du Repertoire des ENtreprises (et de leurs etablissements).

30.name: ISO 6523: Organization identification
30.desc: Partner identification code specified in ISO 6523 (Structures for the identification of organizations).

34.name: National Statistical Agency
34.desc: Partner identification code assigned by a national statistical agency.

51.name: GEIS (General Electric Information Services)
51.desc: Partner identification code assigned by General Electric Information Services.

52.name: INS (IBM Network Services)
52.desc: Partner identification code assigned by IBM Network Services.

53.name: Datenzentrale des Einzelhandels
53.desc: German data centre for retail trade.

55.name: Bank identifier code
55.desc: Partner identification code corresponds to the partner bank identification code.

57.name: KTNet (Korea Trade Network Services)
57.desc: Partner identification code assigned by Korea Trade Network Services.

58.name: UPU (Universal Postal Union)
58.desc: Partner identification code assigned by the Universal Postal Union.

59.name: ODETTE (Organization for Data Exchange through Tele-Transmission in Europe)

61.name: SCAC (Standard Carrier Alpha Code)

86.name: US Council for International Business
86.desc: United States Council for International Business.

87.name: National Federation of Chambers of Commerce and Industry
87.desc: Belgium National Federation of Chambers of Commerce and Industry.

89.name: Association of British Chambers of Commerce
89.desc: Association of British Chambers of Commerce.

91.name: Assigned by seller or seller's agent

92.name: Assigned by buyer or buyer's agent
92.desc: Partner identification code assigned by the buyer or buyer's agent.

103.name: TW, Trade-van

128.name: CH, BCNR (Swiss Clearing Bank Number)
128.desc: Code for the identification of a Swiss clearing bank as a sender and/or receiver of an electronic message.

129.name: CH, BPI (Swiss Business Partner Identification)

144.name: US, DoDAAC (Department of Defense Activity Address Code)
144.desc: Code assigned to uniquely identify all military units in the United States Department of Defense.

145.name: FR, DGCP (Direction Generale de la Comptabilite Publique)
145.desc: Code assigned by the French public accounting office.

146.name: FR, DGI (Direction Generale des Impots)
146.desc: Code assigned by the French taxation authority.

147.name: JP, JIPDEC/ECPC (Japan Information Processing Development Corporation / Electronic Commerce Promotion Center)
147.desc: Partner identification code which is registered with JIPDEC/ECPC.

148.name: ITU (International Telecommunications Union) Data Network Identification Code (DNIC)
148.desc: Data network identification code assigned by the ITU.

Z01.name: Vehicle registration number
Z01.desc: Registration number of a vehicle assigned by a recognised authority.
